---
// src/components/WhyIBuiltThis.astro
---

<section class="why" id="about">
  <div class="why-inner">

    <div class="why-copy">
      <p class="section-tag">Why I built this</p>
      <h2>There was no app<br />built for <em>them</em></h2>

      <div class="why-body">
        <p>
          I've spent years teaching English to adult learners. People with
          jobs, families, and real lives who already speak some English but
          can't seem to break through to the next level.
        </p>
        <p>
          They weren't beginners. They didn't need to learn the alphabet or
          count to ten. What they needed was exposure to real English -- the
          kind spoken in podcasts, at work, and between friends -- and a way
          to practice speaking it without feeling embarrassed.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every app I found was built for beginners. Gamified lessons, cartoon
          characters, basic vocabulary. Nothing designed for someone who already
          knows English but just can't get past that wall.
        </p>
        <p class="why-closer">
          So I built Howdy English. For the learner who's stuck in the middle
          and ready to break through.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="why-founder">
      <div class="why-photo-wrap">
        <img
          src="/screenshots/jeff.jpg"
          alt="Jeff, founder of Howdy English"
          width="120"
          height="120"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          class="why-photo"
        />
      </div>
      <p class="why-name">Jeff</p>
      <p class="why-title">Founder & English Teacher</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why {
    padding: 100px 5%;
    background: #fff;
  }
  .why-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 220px;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .section-tag {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .why-copy h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.2vw, 2.8rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: #111;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .why-copy h2 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: #2563EB;
  }

  .why-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
    max-width: 580px;
  }
  .why-body p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #555;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .why-closer {
    font-size: 1.05rem !important;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #111 !important;
    border-left: 3px solid #2563EB;
    padding-left: 16px;
    margin-top: 8px !important;
  }

  .why-founder {
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(68px + 48px);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding-top: 80px;
  }
  .why-photo-wrap {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 3px solid #EEF3FF;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.12);
    background: #f0f4ff;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .why-photo {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
  .why-name {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .why-title {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #999;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .why-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    .why-founder {
      position: relative;
      top: auto;
      flex-direction: row;
      text-align: left;
      padding-top: 8px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .why-photo-wrap {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .why-body { max-width: 100%; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .why { padding: 70px 5%; }
    .why-closer { font-size: 1rem !important; }
  }

  :global([dir="rtl"]) .why-inner {
    direction: rtl;
  }
  :global([dir="rtl"]) .why-closer {
    border-left: none;
    border-right: 3px solid #2563EB;
    padding-left: 0;
    padding-right: 16px;
  }
</style>
